<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.704.13304.plate70>
    dc:description "Plate 70. Sertitympanum nodosum, female (from Germany), dorsal idiosoma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/158683" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.704.13304.plate71>
    dc:description "Plate 71. Sertitympanum nodosum, female (from Germany). A Dorsal idiosoma B-C Epistome, variant forms D Hypostome, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/158684" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.704.13304.plate76>
    dc:description "Plate 76. Ameroseiidae spp., female. A-E Structures of sperm access system. A Kleemannia delicata, sperm induction pores (solenostomes) associated with inner margin of coxae III B and D Kleemannia plumigera, solenostomes associated with inner margin of coxae III C Epicriopsis suedus, sacculus foemineus and associated tubuli annulati E Sertitympanum nodosum, tubuli annulati F-H Chelicera. F Asperolaelaps rotundus G Ameroseius renatae H Kleemannia delicata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/158689" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.704.13304.plate77>
    dc:description "Plate 77. Ameroseiidae spp., female. A-C Poroid structure associated with peritrematal shield. A Kleemannia delicata B Sertitympanum nodosum C Kleemannia plumigera D Metasternal region in Kleemannia plumigera." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/158690" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

